data.description: Fantastic 4 bedroom, 3 bath brick home on incredible 1.33 acre lot in Jackson Township. Spacious open concept living, dining, and kitchen areas with large picture windows. Kitchen offers lots of counter, cabinet, and storage space. First floor primary bedroom with double closets and plenty of room for separate seating area. Additional bedroom on the first floor. 2 large bedrooms upstairs with built-in desks and loads of storage. Partially finished lower level with two rooms and full bath. Enjoy your private, fully fenced backyard with expansive patio and built-in firepit. Incredibly private and relaxing location, but yet so close to everything!
